replies.body:
Guessed what it was. Clicked it anyway.

What? I like the song!

His voice sounds like it belongs on a black singer.

Not gonna complain, it fits way too well for the song which would probably never be sung by a black artist anyway.

https://i.ytimg.com/vi/uysNTDkwcbE/maxresdefault.jpg
 Because rick rolls and Clickbait are both bad things.
If you wanted to introduce me a sweet ass song, you shoulda just said so.
It's the Memes and Games, you had it coming.
Had what coming? Now if you'll excuse me I'm gonna go checkout this guys other songs, he rocks.
Oh, it's an old fad called "rickrolling" (the guy is named Rick Astley) where people would email each other "important links" to that video. But you aren't wrong, sometimes the classics are the best.
Recognized the link and therefore did not click it... Crisis averted. :^)
